                    Initially, clean energy production was a top priority, due to public interest, time urgency,
                    and lack of progress to date. Land conservation was already high on our agenda.&nbsp;
                    However, systematic analysis revealed an even wider array of needs and solution "best deals."
                  </p>
                  <br>
                  <p>
                    Our standards section shows what our attitude has been toward analyzing our options.&nbsp;
                    Rigorously applying these standards, we reasoned, should result in the best set of priorities.
                  </p>
